!2018-10-21!+V: preterite ;
!2018-10-21!+V+ConNeg+Pl3@U.CONJ-CONNEG.YES@@U.CONJ-NX.PL@@U.CONJ-PX.3@:%>РҪСӢ@U.CONJ-CONNEG.YES@@U.CONJ-NX.PL@@U.CONJ-PX.3@ WordEnd ;
!2018-10-21!+V+ConNeg@U.CONJ-CONNEG.YES@:@U.CONJ-CONNEG.YES@ WordEnd ;

LEXICON EM !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** СҚРј:СҚРј. Ending in -У§СҒСҢ.
@U.CONJ-MX.IND@+Ind+Prs+Sg3:@U.CONJ-MX.IND@ WordEnd ;
+Ind+Prs+Pl3:%>У§СҒСҢ K ; ! Plural predicative ;
+Use/NG+Err/Dial+Ind+Prs+Pl3:%>СҚСҒСҢ K ; ! Plural predicative ;

LEXICON EMYSHT ! СҚРјСӢСҲСӮ "is a little / are a few"
@U.CONJ-MX.IND@+Ind+Prs+Sg3:@U.CONJ-MX.IND@ WordEnd ;
@U.CONJ-MX.IND@@U.CONJ-NX.PL@@U.CONJ-PX.3@+Ind+Prs+Pl3:@U.CONJ-MX.IND@@U.CONJ-NX.PL@@U.CONJ-PX.3@ WordEnd ;
 
LEXICON GER ! 3 lexicalised +Ger forms.
+V+Ger: WordEnd ;

! vim: set ft=xfst-lexc:
